%20the%20hospital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20John%20sat%20with%20his%20mother%20after%20she%20had%20been%20pronounced%20dead%20a%20senior%20nurse%20informed%20him%20of%20the%20mistake.%20Not%20only%20had%20nurses%20checked%20the%20notes%20of%20an%20entirely%20different%20patient%2C%20but%20they%20had%20also%20failed%20to%20check%20the%20NHS%20number%20on%20Ms%20Dawson's%20wristband%2C%20the%20court%20heard.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20had%20not%20even%20confirmed%20her%20age%20and%20gender%20on%20the%20notes.%20The%20patient%20whose%20notes%20were%20confused%20for%20Ms%20Dawson's%20was%20a%2090-year-old%20man%2C%20the%20court%20was%20told.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fchinese-couple-leaves-baby-with-nanny-for-55-million-inheritance-from-ex-partner-5454463%5C%22%3EChinese%20Couple%20Leaves%20Baby%20With%20Nanny%20For%20%2455%20Million%20Inheritance%20From%20Ex-Partner%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20tragically%20and%20catastrophically%20these%20were%20not%20Pat's%20records%3B%20they%20belonged%20to%20an%20entirely%20different%20patient%20who%20was%20male%20and%20in%20his%2090s%3B%20characteristics%20which%20Pat%20very%20clearly%20did%20not%20share%2C%26quot%3B%20Area%20Coroner%20Kate%20Bisset%20said%2C%20as%20per%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BIt%20was%20quickly%20realised%20that%20a%20DNR%20was%20not%20in%20place%20however%2C%20tragically%2C%20it%20was%20too%20late%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmergency%20consultant%20Dr%20Ahmad%20Alabood%20told%20the%20inquest%20it%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Bhonest%20mistake%20because%20(staff)%20were%20rushing%26quot%3B.%20He%20admitted%20that%20it%20is%20probable%20that%20Ms%20Dawson%20would%20have%20been%20resuscitated%20had%20medics%20attempted%20to%20do%20so.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20ruled%20of%20neglect%20and%20concluded%20that%20Ms%20Dawson%20would%20not%20have%20died%20when%20she%20did%20if%20these%20mistakes%20had%20not%20been%20made.%20Royal%20Blackburn%20Hospital%20has%20also%20implemented%20several%20systemic%20changes%20since%20the%2073-year-old's%20death%20after%20an%20internal%20investigation%20flagged%20various%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713321240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-12%2F2sa26v_uk-ambulance-reuters_625x300_14_December_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-woman-73-dies-after-medics-check-do-not-resuscitate-notice-of-wrong-patient-5459165%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20fit%20and%20healthy%20retired%20nurse%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20died%20after%20staff%20at%20a%20hospital%20checked%20the%20wrong%20patient's%20notes%20which%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bdo%20not%20resuscitate%26quot%3B%20order%20in%20place.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-woman-73-dies-after-medics-check-do-not-resuscitate-notice-of-wrong-patient-5459165%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-woman-73-dies-after-medics-check-do-not-resuscitate-notice-of-wrong-patient-5459165%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-woman-73-dies-after-medics-check-do-not-resuscitate-notice-of-wrong-patient-5459165%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Biblical-level%20flooding%3A%20Chaos%20in%20Dubai%3B%20flights%20hit%2C%20families%20stranded%20at%20airport%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713321151000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109361087%2Cimgsize-1282730.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fexceptional-weather-hits-gulf-flight-operations-hit-in-dubai%2Farticleshow%2F109360936.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20heavy%20rains%20that%20caused%20the%20suspensions%20and%20diversions%20are%20part%20of%20broader%20adverse%20weather%20conditions%20affecting%20the%20Gulf%20Peninsula.%20In%20Oman%2C%20heavy%20rainfall%20has%20led%20to%20tragic%20consequences%20with%20at%20least%2018%20fatalities%20reported%20in%20recent%20days.%20Dubai%20itself%20faced%20unprecedented%20flooding%2C%20impacting%20transportation%2C%20retail%20locations%20like%20Dubai%20Mall%20and%20Mall%20of%20the%20Emirates%2C%20and%20even%20the%20metro%20system%20where%20water%20pooled%20ankle-deep%20in%20some%20stations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20WORLD%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Envoy's%20Rejoinder%20To%20Ireland%20Daily%20Angers%20Congress%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20objected%20to%20an%20Indian%20envoy%20accusing%20a%20%26quot%3Bsingle%20dynastic%20party%26quot%3B%20of%20corruption%20in%20remarks%20published%20in%20a%20leading%20Irish%20daily.%20Akhilesh%20Mishra%2C%20the%20Indian%20ambassador%20to%20Ireland%2C%20made%20the%20remarks%20in%20a%20rejoinder%20after%20the%20embassy%20termed%20an%20editorial%20published%20in%20The%20Irish%20Times%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20biased%20and%20prejudiced%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20denounced%20the%20remarks%20and%20said%20that%20an%20ambassador%20is%20not%20expected%20to%20attack%20the%20Opposition%20openly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20editorial%20%26quot%3BModi%20tightens%20his%20grip%26quot%3B%2C%20while%20predicting%20a%20comfortable%20third%20term%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20mentioned%20the%20arrest%20of%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20tax%20cases%20against%20opposition%20leaders.%20Contesting%20the%20claims%2C%20the%20Indian%20embassy%20said%20it%20cast%20aspersions%20on%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20democracy%2C%20law%20enforcement%20institutions%2C%20and%20the%20%26quot%3BHindu-majority%26quot%3B%20people%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20rejoinder%2C%20Mr%20Mishra%20praised%20the%20Modi%20government's%20fight%20against%20corruption%20that%20he%20blamed%20on%20the%20%26quot%3B55-year%20misrule%20by%20a%20single%20dynastic%20party%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fight%20against%20the%20deeply%20entrenched%20ecosystem%20of%20corruption%20(created%20by%20the%2055-year%20rule%2C%20including%20first%2030%20years%2C%20by%20a%20single%20dynastic%20party%20in%20India)%20is%20a%20major%20factor%20behind%20Mr%20Modi's%20ever-growing%20popularity.%20There%20is%20huge%20sense%20of%20relief%20at%20the%20grass-root%20level%20to%20witness%20action%20being%20taken%20and%20recoveries%20made%20from%20the%20rich%20and%20powerful%20elites%20who%20operated%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20entitlement%20of%20impunity%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Mishra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20prompt%20backlash%2C%20the%20Congress's%20communications%20in-charge%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20questioned%20the%20ambassador's%20%26quot%3Bunprofessional%20and%20disgraceful%20behaviour%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDefending%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20is%20one%20thing%20and%20is%20to%20be%20expected.%20But%20to%20attack%20Opposition%20parties%20openly%20in%20this%20manner%20like%20a%20party%20apparatchik%20is%20not%20expected%20from%20an%20Ambassador%20even%20if%20he%20be%20a%20political%20appointment.%20This%20is%20unprofessional%20and%20disgraceful%20behaviour%20on%20his%20part-but%20is%20par%20for%20the%20Modi%20course%20I%20guess%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Ramesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20follow-up%20post%2C%20he%20said%20the%20ambassador%20breached%20his%20service%20rules%20and%20should%20be%20sacked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20stand%20corrected.%20This%20Ambassador%20is%20actually%20a%20career%20diplomat%20which%20makes%20his%20comments%20even%20more%20shameful%2C%20disgraceful%20and%20completely%20unacceptable.%20He%20has%20actually%20breached%20service%20rules%20and%20should%20be%20sacked%20right%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20the%20senior%20Congress%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mishra%2C%20an%20Indian%20Foreign%20Service%20officer%20of%20the%201989%20batch%2C%20was%20posted%20as%20the%20Indian%20ambassador%20to%20Ireland%20in%20Dublin%20in%20October%202021.%20He%20posted%20an%20Officer%20on%20Special%20Duty%20in%20the%20foreign%20ministry%20prior%20to%20this.%20He%20has%20also%20served%20as%20the%20ambassador%20to%20Maldives%20(2016-19)%2C%20Consul%20General%20in%20Toronto%20(2013-16)%2C%20and%20Deputy%20Chief%20of%20Mission%20in%20Kabul%20(2008-10).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713321120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F6hevs87_akhilesh-mishra-ifs_625x300_17_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-envoys-rejoinder-to-ireland-daily-angers-congress-5459164%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20has%20objected%20to%20an%20Indian%20envoy%20accusing%20a%20%26quot%3Bsingle%20dynastic%20party%26quot%3B%20of%20corruption%20in%20remarks%20published%20in%20a%20leading%20Irish%20daily.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-envoys-rejoinder-to-ireland-daily-angers-congress-5459164%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-envoys-rejoinder-to-ireland-daily-angers-congress-5459164%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-envoys-rejoinder-to-ireland-daily-angers-congress-5459164%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SRK%20breaks%20down%20after%20cricket%20team's%20loss%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713321079000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109360690%2Cimgsize-21758.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%