to%20the%20middle%20of%20this.%20But%20we%20do%20encourage%20both%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20to%20avoid%20escalation%20and%20find%20a%20resolution%20through%20dialogue.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMiller%2C%20while%20addressing%20a%20press%20briefing%2C%20said%20that%20he%20will%20never%20preview%20any%20sanction%20actions%20and%20that%20the%20%26quot%3BUS%20does%20not%20discuss%20sanctions%20openly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20why%20the%20US%20has%20not%20imposed%20any%20sanctions%20on%20India%20over%20the%20alleged%20assassination%20plot%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%20Miller%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20never%20going%20to%20preview%20any%20sanction%20actions%2C%20which%20is%20not%20to%20say%20that%20there%20are%20any%20coming%2C%20but%20when%20you%20ask%20me%20to%20talk%20about%20sanctions%2C%20it's%20something%20that%20we%20don't%20discuss%20openly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%20is%20an%20India-designated%20terrorist%20and%20has%20repeatedly%20issued%20threats%20against%20India.%20As%20per%20the%20US%20Justice%20Department%20indictment%2C%20an%20Indian%20national%2C%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20in%20custody%2C%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20the%20murder-for-hire%20of%20Pannun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Justice%20Department%20had%20earlier%20claimed%20that%20an%20Indian%20government%20employee%2C%20who%20was%20not%20identified%20in%20the%20indictment%20filed%2C%20had%20recruited%20Gupta%20to%20hire%20a%20hitman%20to%20allegedly%20assassinate%20Pannun%2C%20which%20was%20foiled%20by%20US%20authorities.%20Last%20year%2C%20India%20formed%20a%20committee%20to%20inquire%20into%20the%20allegations%20of%20the%20foiled%20assassination%20plot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%2011%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20that%20in%20the%2010%20years%20of%20the%20BJP%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20%26quot%3Bterrorists%20are%20being%20killed%20in%20their%20own%20homes.%26quot%3B%20Addressing%20a%20public%20rally%20in%20Uttarakhand's%20Rishikesh%2C%20PM%20Modi%20highlighted%20the%20major%20decisions%20taken%20by%20his%20government%2C%20emphasising%20that%20it%20was%20under%20the%20NDA%20regime%20that%20Article%20370%20was%20abrogated%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20there%20is%20a%20strong%20government%20in%20the%20country.%20Under%20this%20'mazboot%20Modi%20sarkar%2C%20aatankwaadiyon%20ko%20ghar%20mein%20ghus%20ke%20mara%20jata%20hai'.%20The%20Indian%20tricolour%20has%20become%20a%20guarantee%20of%20security%20even%20in%20the%20war%20zone.%20After%20seven%20decades%2C%20Article%20370%20was%20scrapped%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20a%20law%20was%20made%20against%20triple%20talaq.%20It%20was%20our%20strong%20government%20that%20ensured%2033%20per%20cent%20reservation%20in%20Parliament%20and%20the%20poor%20in%20the%20general%20category%20also%20got%2010%20per%20cent%20reservation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PM%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20repeatedly%20emphasised%20that%20it%20will%20not%20tolerate%20cross-border%20terrorism%20and%20that%20it%20cannot%20keep%20aside%20terrorism%20to%20improve%20ties%20with%20Islamabad.%20New%20Delhi%20has%20also%20said%20the%20onus%20is%20on%20Islamabad%20to%20create%20a%20conducive%20atmosphere%20in%20which%20there%20is%20no%20terror%2C%20hostility%2C%20or%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20ANI%2C%20Rajnath%20Singh%20said%20if%20Pakistan's%20intention%20is%20clear%2C%20it%20should%20act%20decisively%20against%20cross-border%20terrorism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Pakistan%20attempts%20to%20destabilise%20India%20through%20terrorism%2C%20it%20will%20have%20to%20face%20the%20consequences.%20Pakistan%20needs%20to%20control%20terrorism.%20If%20Pakistan%20thinks%20that%20it%20is%20not%20capable%20of%20controlling%20it%2C%20if%20they%20feel%20they%20are%20not%20capable%2C%20then%20India%20is%20a%20neighbour%2C%20if%20they%20