ould%20completely%20scrap%20the%20idea%20of%20having%20different%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20beauty%20of%20athletics%20and%20women%20is%20we're%20not%20a%20monolith%2C%26quot%3B%20Harrison-Claye%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20some%20women%2C%20they%20can%20see%20that%20and%20be%20like%2C%20'Oh%2C%20I%20will%20feel%20so%20cool%2C%20and%20I'll%20feel%20sexy%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20they%20have%20that%20right%20to%20feel%20like%20themselves%20%E2%80%A6%20and%20then%20there%20will%20be%20a%20lot%20of%20female%20athletes%20that%20are%20like%2C%20'Oh%20no%2C%20this%20cut%20is%20too%20small.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Queen%20Harrison-Claye%20in%20blue%20makeup%2C%20a%20blue%20Team%20USA%20jacket%2C%20and%20blue%20hairclips%2C%20holds%20up%20a%20blue%20medal%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661ef94049058e669356c3ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EQueen%20Harrison-Claye%20during%20the%202018%20Athletics%20World%20Cup%20London%3Cp%3EMarc%20Atkins%20-%20British%20Athletics%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20athletes%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdivision-1-female-athletes-plagued-with-eating-disorders-missing-periods-2019-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELauren%20Fleshman%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20retired%20runner%20and%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BGood%20for%20a%20Girl%3A%20A%20Woman%20Running%20in%20a%20Man's%20World%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20that%20she%20took%20issue%20with%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20company%20chose%20to%20preview%20the%20revealing%20women's%20suit%20alongside%20the%20covered-up%20men's%20suit%20%E2%80%94%20instead%20of%20displaying%20two%20similar%20suits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20are%20we%20presenting%20this%20sexualized%20outfit%20as%20the%20standard%20of%20excellence%3F%26quot%3B%20Fleshman%20told%20the