20Security%20Force%20(BSF)%20and%20the%20state%20police's%20District%20Reserve%20Guard%20(DRG).%20Three%20people%20were%20injured%20-%20two%20from%20the%20BSF%20and%20one%20from%20the%20DRG.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minute-long%20video%20shows%20security%20personnel%20walking%20through%20the%20jungle%20when%20suddenly%2C%2020%20seconds%20in%2C%20one%20of%20them%20fires%20two%20shots%20from%20his%20rifle.%20Shouting%20is%20heard%20from%20various%20sides%20and%20the%20man%20shooting%20the%20video%20then%20warns%20personnel%20ahead%20of%20him%20to%20tread%20carefully%20and%20not%20rush%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EPeeche%20se%20koi%20fire%20nahin%20karega%20bhai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(no%20one%20should%20fire%20from%20behind)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20warns%20his%20fellow%20personnel%20and%20the%20video%20ends%20with%20him%20repeating%20the%20warning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20involved%20in%20the%20encounter%20was%20led%20by%20Laxman%20Kewat%2C%20a%20President's%20Award%20winner%20who%20has%20also%20been%20honoured%20with%20six%20other%20awards.%20Known%20as%20an%20encounter%20specialist%2C%20he%20has%20killed%2044%20Maoists%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Planning%20Big%20Incident'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%20evening%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20Chief%20Minister%20Vishnu%20Deo%20Sai%20said%20the%20operation%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bbiggest-ever%20success%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20state's%20fight%20against%20Maoists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20congratulate%20everyone%20involved%20in%20the%20operation%20and%20salute%20their%20courage.%20Maoists%20don't%20believe%20in%20democracy%20and%20it%20is%20possible%20that%20they%20were%20looking%20to%20influence%20the%20elections.%20The%20place%20where%20the%20gunfight%20took%20place%20is%20near%20both%20the%20Bastar%20and%20Kanker%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituencies%2C%20and%20Bastar%20will%20vote%20in%20the%20first%20phase%20on%20Friday...%20They%20were%20attempting%20to%20carry%20out%20a%20big%20incident%20and%20their%20plans%20have%20been%20foiled%20by%20the%20security%20forces%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sai%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHome%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20also%20called%20for%2C%20and%20taken%20a%20pledge%20for%2C%20a%20Maoist-free%20Bastar%20region.%20This%20operation%20is%20a%20big%20success%20towards%20ensuring%20peace.%20The%20government%20wishes%20to%20end%20the%20bloodshed%20and%20would%20like%20the%20Maoists%20to%20leave%20the%20path%20of%20violence%2C%20hold%20talks%20and%20join%20the%20path%20of%20development...%20The%20three%20injured%20personnel%20are%20out%20of%20danger%20and%20are%20undergoing%20treatment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713316920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fsmdrpfbg_chhattisgarh-maoist-encounter_625x300_17_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsilence-footsteps-and-then-gunfire-behind-the-scenes-of-maoist-encounter-5457742%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20video%20shot%20by%20a%20security%20personnel%20shows%20a%20glimpse%20of%20what%20it%20took%20to%20carry%20out%20Chhattisgarh's%20biggest%20anti-Maoist%20operation%2C%20which%20left%2029%20rebels%20dead.%20The%20dead%20Maoists%20included%20a%20senior%20leader%2C%20Shankar%20Rao%2C%20who%20had%20a%20bounty%20of%20Rs%2025%20lakh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsilence-footsteps-and-then-gunfire-behind-the-scenes-of-maoist-encounter-5457742%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsilence-footsteps-and-then-gunfire-behind-the-scenes-of-maoist-encounter-5457742%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsilence-footsteps-and-then-gunfire-behind-the-scenes-of-maoist-encounter-5457742%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%3A%20Dubai%20Airport%20Flooded%2C%20Flights%20D