20a%20home%20is%20not%20the%20only%20way%20to%20build%20wealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERenting%20is%20not%20a%20waste%20of%20time%20and%20money%20%E2%80%94%20and%20more%20and%20more%20people%20are%20realizing%20this.%20A%20study%20released%20earlier%20this%20year%20by%20the%20apartment%20listing%20service%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rentcafe.com%2Fblog%2Frental-market%2Fmarket-snapshots%2Fmillionaire-renter-households-triple-in-numbers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERentCafe%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20using%20data%20from%20the%20US%20Census%20Bureau%2C%20found%20that%20the%20number%20of%20high-income%20renters%20making%20%24150%2C000%20or%20more%20jumped%2082%25%20between%202015%20and%202020%2C%20while%20the%20number%20of%20millionaire%20renter%20households%20tripled%20during%20that%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20does%20this%20mean%3F%20Like%20I%20always%20say%2C%20personal%20finance%20is%20personal%2C%20and%20there%20are%20no%20hard%20and%20fast%20rules%20for%20financial%20success.%20Don't%20rush%20into%20homeownership%20thinking%20that%20it%20is%20the%20fastest%20way%20or%20the%20only%20way%20to%20build%20wealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20owned%20a%20home%20for%20seven%20years%2C%20but%20now%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Frenting-after-homeownership-love-2023-8%5C%22%3EI'm%20happy%20as%20a%20renter%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Here%20are%20a%20few%20things%20I%20learned%20after%20going%20from%20owning%20a%20home%20to%20renting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E1.%20Renters%20have%20fewer%20hidden%20costs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20thinking%20about%20buying%20a%20home%20and%20then%20going%20through%20the%20purchase%20process%2C%20I%20was%20solely%20focused%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-much-down-payment-for-a-house%5C%22%3Edown%20payment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20moving%2C%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20monthly%20mortgage%20payments.%20But%20once%20I%20was%20in%20the%20home%2C%20there%20was%20so%20much%20more%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3Eway%3C%2Fem%3E%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-homeowners-insurance-companies%5C%22%3Ehomeowners%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20property%20taxes%2C%20and%20maintenance%20and%20upkeep.%20These%20are%20the%20costs%20that%20people%20never%20talk%20about.%20It's%20not%20just%20about%20the%20monthly%20mortgage%20payment.%20When%20I%20moved%20into%20my%20home%2C%20I%20immediately%20had%20serious%20work%20to%20do%20to%20stop%20a%20leaking%20roof.%20I%20honestly%20felt%20like%20the%20previous%20homeowner%20held%20the%20house%20together%20with%20paper%20clips%20and%20tape%20just%20long%20enough%20to%20sell%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20as%20a%20renter%2C%20there%20aren't%20any%20%26quot%3Bhidden%20costs%2C%26quot%3B%20no%20expenses%20around%20maintenance%20and%20upkeep%2C%20and%20no%20property%20taxes%20or%20insurance.%20Yes%2C%20I%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-renters-insurance-companies%5C%22%3Erenters%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20it%20costs%20a%20fraction%20of%20what%20I%20used%20to%20pay%20for%20property%20insurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E2.%20Renters%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20inflation's%20impact%20on%20the%20housing%20market%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20increase%20in%20the%20federal%20funds%20rate%20can%20cause%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2F30-year-mortgage-rates%5C%22%3Emortgage%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20rise.%20When%20mortgage%20rates%20rise%2C%20that%20leads%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20monthly%20payments%20for%20a%20loan%20of%20the%20same%20amount.%20For%20example%2C%20at%20a%204%25%20interest%20rate%2C%20a%20%24300%2C000%20mortgage%20would%20cost%20%241%2C432%20a%20month.%20At%206%25%2C%20the%20same%20loan%20would%20cost%20%241%2C799%20a%20month.%20The%20effects%20are%20greater%20on%20larger%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20increases%20affect%20a%20seller's%20ability%20to%20sell%20and%20a%20buyer's%20ability%20to%20buy.%20Renting%20right%20now%20puts%20me%20in%20a%20place%20where%20I%20am%20a%20happy%20spectator%20to%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20the%20housing%20market.%20While%20I%20am%20still%20dealing%20with%20the%20effects%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-inflation%5C%22%3Einflation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20is%20from%20a%20much%20different%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E3.%20Homeownership%20is%20not%20the%20marker%20of%20achievement%20it%20used%20to%20be%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Cspan%3EGoDaddy%20survey%3C%2Fspan%3E%20asked%201%2C000%20small%20business%20owners%20to%20describe%20what%20achieving%20the%20American%20dream%20means%20to%20them.%2054%25%20responded%20that%20it%20means%20feeling%20happy%20in%20life%2C%20and%2049%25%20said%20freedom%20to%20follow%20their%20passions.%20Homeownership%2C%20historically%20seen%20as%20a%20marker%20of%20success%2C%20was%20fourth%20on%20the%20list%20at%2045%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20the%20American%20dream%20to%20me%3F%20Living%20the%20life%20that%20I%20am%20living%20with%20freedom%2C%20flexibility%2C%20comfort%2C%20and%20financial%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20again%2C%20I%20am%20not%20saying%20that%20owning%20a%20home%20or%20wanting%20to%20own%20a%20home%20is%20a%20bad%20thing%20%E2%80%94%20I%20fully%20intend%20to%20own%20a%20home%20again.%20I%20am%20saying%2C%20however%2C%20that%20owning%20a%20home%20is%20not%20the%20only%20indicator%20of%20success%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20the%20only%20way%20to%20build%20wealth%20is%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprises-owning-home-renting-2024-04%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713304201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64df