%20college%20entrance%20exam%20scoring%20information%20for%20PLA%20%5BPeople's%20Liberation%20Army%5D%20academic%20institutions%2C%20the%20PLAN%20Engineering%20University%20on%20average%20ranks%20number%20two%20on%20test%20scores%20across%20PLA%20academic%20institutions%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdigital-commons.usnwc.edu%2Fcgi%2Fviewcontent.cgi%3Farticle%3D1026%26context%3Dcmsi-maritime-reports%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epaper%3C%2Fa%3E%20written%20by%20Roderick%20Lee%2C%20an%20expert%20on%20the%20Chinese%20military%2C%20for%20the%20China%20Maritime%20Studies%20Institute%20at%20the%20US%20Naval%20War%20College.%20%26quot%3BMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Submarine%20Academy%20consistently%20ranks%20among%20the%20bottom%20three%20of%20all%20PLA%20institutions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAssuming%20a%20student's%20%3Cem%3EGaokao%3C%2Fem%3E%20score%20is%20generally%20indicative%20of%20overall%20performance%20potential%2C%20this%20suggests%20that%20PLAN%20submarine%20officer%20cadets%20tracking%20towards%20non-engineering%20department%20positions%20are%20inferior%20to%20their%20engineering%20brethren%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERivalry%20between%20the%20engineers%20on%20the%20lower%20decks%20who%20keep%20the%20ship's%20engines%20running%2C%20versus%20bridge%20officers%20such%20as%20captains%2C%20navigators%20and%20weapons%20officers%2C%20isn't%20unusual%20in%20any%20navy%3B%20in%20the%20US%2C%20by%20contrast%2C%20all%20submarine%20officers%20and%20commanders%20are%20trained%20in%20nuclear%20engineering.%20By%20the%20time%20a%20Chinese%20officer%20reaches%20submarine%20command%2C%20they've%20had%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20of%20training%20and%20fleet%20experience%20since%20taking%20their%20college%20entry%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20selectivity%20disparity%20inside%20the%20Chinese%20navy%20is%20remarkable%2C%20given%20that%20submarines%20would%20be%20one%20of%20China's%20most%20important%20weapons%20in%20a%20conflict%20with%20the%20US%2C%20Japan%20or%20Taiwan.%20The%20PLAN%20currently%20operates%20around%2060%20submarines%2C%20including%206%20armed%20with%20nuclear-tipped%20ballistic%20missiles%2C%20plus%206%20nuclear-%20and%2046%20diesel-powered%20attack%20subs%20armed%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20anti-ship%20missiles%20and%20torpedoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20academic%20prowess%20equates%20to%20military%20competence%20has%20always%20been%20up%20for%20debate.%20History%20is%20full%20of%20commanders%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20George%20McClellan%20in%20the%20American%20Civil%20War%20%E2%80%94%20who%20proved%20more%20impressive%20in%20the%20classroom%20than%20on%20the%20battlefield.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20legendary%20George%20Patton%20nearly%20flunked%20out%20of%20West%20Point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegardless%2C%20the%20Chinese%20navy%20seems%20to%20have%20had%20doubts%20about%20those%20commanding%20its%20surface%20ships%20and%20submarines%3A%20higher-level%20officers%20would%20often%20sail%20with%20them%20to%20supervise.%20%26quot%3BHistorically%2C%20a%20PLAN%20submarine%20captain's%20authority%20could%20be%20eroded%20by%20the%20presence%20of%20more%20senior%20officers%20onboard%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20noted.%20%26quot%3BThe%20issue%20of%20flotilla-level%20leadership%20deploying%20to%20single-ship%20formations%20and%20'babysitting'%20ship%20captains%20was%20such%20an%20issue%20for%20the%20PLAN%20surface%20fleet%20that%20the%20PLAN%20explicitly%20prohibited%20the%20practice%20in%202019.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20clear%20to%20what%20degree%20senior%20officers%20continue%20to%20babysit%20submarine%20skippers%2C%20who%20already%20have%20to%20share%20authority%20with%20a%20political%20commissar%20aboard%20each%20vessel.%20There%20is%20evidence%20that%20having%20a%20senior%20officer%20effectively%20take%20command%20of%20a%20submarine%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjamestown.org%2Fprogram%2Ftrust-deficit-in-pla-navy-submarine-command-origins-and-consequences%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebreeds%20resentment%3C%2Fa%3E%20among%20a%20sub's%20crew.%20Perhaps%20not%20coincidentally%2C%20Lee%20notes%20that%20flotilla%20commanders%20and%20staff%20were%20aboard%20when%20the%20Ming-class%20diesel%20sub%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2003%2FWORLD%2Fasiapcf%2Feast%2F05%2F02%2Fchina.submarine%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESS-361%3C%2Fa%3E%20sank%20in%202003%2C%20as%20well%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2Farticle%2F1584450%2Fpla-reveals-how-captain-stopped-submarine-falling-3000-metre-trench%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enear-loss%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Kilo-class%20SS-372%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22chinese%20submarine%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5407724aeab8eab611fded2c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChinese%20sailors%20salute%20on%20top%20of%20a%20submarine%20during%20the%20fleet's%20review%20of%20the%20China-Russia%20joint%20naval%20exercise%20in%20the%20Yellow%20Sea%20on%20April%2026%2C%202012.%3Cp%3EChina%20Daily%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESubmarine%20duty%20is%20already%20arduous%20and%20isolating%2C%20and%20command%20conflicts%20only%20exacerbate%20what%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20mental%20health%20crisis%20among%20Chinese%20commanders%20and%20crews.%20When%20researchers%20from%20China's%20Second%20Military%20Medical%20University%20conducted%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facademic.oup.com%2Fmilmed%2Farticle%2F187%2F5-6%2Fe696%2F6067548%3Flogin%3Dfalse%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurvey%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202021%20of%20submarine%20crews%20in%20the%20PLAN's%20South%20China%20Sea%20fleet%20crews%2C%2021%20percent%20reported%20experiencing%20mental%20health%20issues.%20Sailors%20and%20officers%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20submarine%20force%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%20are%20facing%20mental%20health%20risks%20and%20suffering%20from%20serious%20psychological%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20concluded%20the%20study%2C%20which%20listed%20education%20%E2%80%94%20along%20with%20age%20and%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20as%20the%20best%20predictors%20of%20mental%20health%20for%20sub%20crews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLife%20in%20the%20PLAN%20submarine%20service%20is%20difficult%2C%26quot%3B%20Christopher%C2%A0Sharman%2C%20director%20of%20the%20China%20Maritime%20Studies%20Institute%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BConditions%20are%20challenging%20and%20China%20has%20suffered%20submarine%20accidents%20in%20the%20past.%C2%A0%20These%20variables%20contribute%20to%20making%20a%20life%20in%20the%20submarine%20force%20less%20attractive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20thought%20of%20a%20submarine%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20one%20powered%20by%20a%20nuclear%20reactor%20or%20even%20armed%20with%20nuclear%20missiles%20%E2%80%94%20being%20commanded%20by%20an%20officer%20with%20a%20low%20SAT%20score%20is%20less%20than%20reassuring.%20Nonetheless%2C%20Lee%20believes%20that%20China's%20submarine%20fleet%20is%20still%20a%20capable%20force.%20There%20are%20%26quot%3Bno%20clear%20and%20glaring%20flaws%20in%20how%20the%20PLAN%20leads%20its%20submarine%20force.%20Although%20its%20educational%20system%20underwent%20some%20turmoil%20in%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%2021st%20century%20and%20continues%20to%20encounter%20challenges%20today%2C%20these%20challenges%20do%20not%20appear%20to%20be%20substantial%20enough%20to%20dramatically%20affect%20operational%20performance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20the%20poor%20educational%20qualifications%20of%20Chinese%20sub%20skippers%20may%20be%20a%20vulnerability%20that%20US%20anti-submarines%20can%20exploit%2C%20Lee%20suggests.%20China's%20submarine%20force%20is%20more%20likely%20to%20make%20mistakes%20since%20it%20%26quot%3Bdraws%20its%20leaders%20from%20some%20of%20the%20worst-performing%20officer%20cadets%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20said.%20%26quot%3BEven%20if%20the%20%3Cem%3EGaokao%3C%2Fem%3E%20score%20is%20not%20indicative%20of%20overall%20human%20performance%2C%20it%20does%20reflect%20some%20level%20of%20intelligence%20and%20individual%20dedication.%20The%20PLAN%20submarine%20force%20must%20therefore%20rely%20on%20its%20least%20talented%20officers%20to%20lead%20forces%20that%20may%20be%20cut%20off%20for%20days%20if%20not%20weeks%20at%20a%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20stressing%20Chinese%20submarine%20commanders%2C%20such%20as%20confronting%20them%20with%20multiple%20or%20unexpected%20challenges%2C%20they%20could%20be%20goaded%20into%20making%20a%20mistake.%20%26quot%3BThis%20may%20make%20PLAN%20submarine%20officers%20more%20likely%20to%20suffer%20from%20the%20error%20precursors%20of%20poor%20proficiency%2C%20poor%20problem-solving%20skills%2C%20inappropriate%20attitudes%20towards%20tasks%2C%20imprecise%20communication%20habits%2C%20and%20inability%20to%20handle%20stress.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20a%20Chinese%20submarine%20captain%20will%20have%20had%20years%20of%20experience%20and%20additional%20training%20before%20assuming%20command.%20It%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20if%20his%20college%20test%20scores%20impact%20his%20combat%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMichael%20Peck%20is%20a%20defense%20writer%20whose%20work%20has%20appeared%20in%20Forbes%2C%20Defense%20News%2C%20Foreign%20Policy%20magazine%2C%20and%20other%20publications.%20He%20holds%20an%20MA%20in%20political%20science%20from%20Rutgers%20Univ.%20Follow%20him%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitter.com%2F%40mipeck1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETwitter%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fmipeck%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELinkedIn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20art