20been%20tied%20to%20the%20banister.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20police%20arrested%20Pan%20after%20her%20father%2C%20who%20survived%20the%20shooting%2C%20was%20able%20to%20recount%20his%20experience%20of%20the%20incident.%20And%20after%20a%20lengthy%20trial%20in%202014%2C%20Pan%20and%20three%20other%20co-accused%20(including%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhere-is-daniel-wong-now-jennifer-pan-ex-boyfriend-netflix-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eformer%20boyfriend%2C%20Daniel%20Wong%3C%2Fa%3E)%20were%20found%20guilty%20of%20first-degree%20murder%20and%20attempted%20murder%2C%20and%20received%20life%20in%20prison%20sentences%20with%20no%20chance%20of%20parole%20for%2025%20years.%20However%2C%20an%20appeals%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fcanada%2Ftoronto%2Fjennifer-pan-new-trial-1.6849590%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eordered%20a%20retrial%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20first-degree%20murder%20charge%2C%20and%20the%20case%20currently%20sits%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yorkregion.com%2Fnews%2Fcrime%2Fits-a-fine-line-crown-seeks-supreme-court-appeal-in-jennifer-pan-case%2Farticle_276d18c7-fee8-52c6-a8ff-9dbc60834cf2.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%20of%20Canada%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHann%20Pan%20was%20granted%20a%20non-communication%20order%20following%20the%20trial.%20Here's%20where%20he%20is%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHann%20Pan%20survived%20the%20home%20invasion%20that%20the%20court%20found%20his%20daughter%20guilty%20of%20orchestrating%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EReporter%20Karen%20K.%20Ho%2C%20who%20grew%20up%20with%20Pan%20and%20Wong%2C%20reported%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftorontolife.com%2Fcity%2Fjennifer-pan-revenge%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EToronto%20Life%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Hann%20Pan%20immigrated%20to%20Canada%20from%20Vietnam%20in%201979%20as%20a%20refugee%2C%20and%20married%20his%20wife%20Bich%20Ha%20Pan%20in%20Toronto.%20They%20had%20two%20children%3A%20Jennifer%20in%201986%2C%20and%20a%20son%20named%20Felix%20in%201989.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToronto%20Life's%20account%20of%20Pan's%20childhood%20recounts%20the%20pressure%20that%20Hann%20and%20Bich%20placed%20on%20her%20to%20excel%20in%20academics%20and%20extracurriculars%2C%20including%20piano%20and%20figure%20skating.%20Hann%2C%20per%20the%20publication%2C%20prevented%20her%20from%20attending%20school%20dances%20and%20parties%2C%20as%20well%20as%20dating.%20As%20Pan%20grew%20older%2C%20her%20academic%20performance%20turned%20average%2C%20and%20she%20began%20to%20lie%20to%20her%20parents%20about%20her%20grades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20she%20lied%20to%20them%20about%20attending%20university%2C%20instead%20secretly%20working%20several%20jobs%20while%20pretending%20to%20go%20to%20class.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20she%20lived%20part-time%20with%20Wong's%20family%2C%20telling%20her%20parents%20that%20she%20was%20staying%20with%20a%20friend%20in%20the%20city%20during%20the%20school%20week.%20After%20she%20lied%20about%20working%20a%20volunteer%20job%2C%20they%20followed%20her%20and%20learned%20that%20she%20hadn't%20been%20employed%20there.%20The%20lies%20fell%20apart%2C%20and%20Pan's%20parents%20told%20her%20she%20couldn't%20see%20Wong%20and%20placed%20restrictions%20on%20her%20travel%20and%20communication%2C%20according%20to%20Toronto%20Life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202010%2C%20Pan%20began%20to%20plot%20her%20parents'%20murder%2C%20hiring%20Lenford%20Crawford%2C%20one%20of%20Wong's%20acquaintances.%20Hann%20survived%20the%20November%202010%20incident%20and%20was%20placed%20in%20a%20three-day%20medically%20induced%20coma.%20Pan%20underwent%20two%20interviews%20with%20police%2C%20which%20are%20depicted%20at%20length%20in%20%26quot%3BWhat%20Jennifer%20Did%2C%26quot%3B%20maintaining%20that%20she%20was%20also%20a%20victim%20of%20the%20break-in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20Hann%20woke%20up%2C%20his%20testimony%20contradicted%20some%20of%20what%20his%20daughter%20had%20told%20police.%20Specifically%2C%20he%20remembered%20her%20speaking%20amiably%20with%20one%20of%20the%20men%20who%20entered%20the%20Pan%20household%2C%20and%20that%20she%20was%20walking%20around%20unbound%20during%20the%20invasion.%20Police%20brought%20Pan%20in%20for%20a%20third%20interview%2C%20also%20seen%20in%20the%20documentary%2C%20and%20ultimately%20arrested%20her.%20They%20arrested%20Wong%2C%20Crawford%2C%20and%20two%20other%20men%20involved%20in%20the%20break-in%20in%20early%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHann%20Pan%20testified%20during%20his%20daughter's%20trial%20and%20requested%20no%20communication%20from%20her%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPan's%20trial%20began%20in%202014%20and%20lasted%20almost%2010%20months%2C%20according%20to%20Toronto%20Life.%20Per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fcanada%2Ftoronto%2Fjennifer-pan-s-father-testifies-at-murder-trial-1.2585146%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECBC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20and%20her%20co-accused%20pleaded%20not%20guilty.%20Hann%20Pan%20testified%20during%20the%20trial%20about%20what%20he%20recalled%20from%20the%20night%20of%20his%20wife's%20murder%2C%20and%20other%20circumstances%20of%20Pan's%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20very%20upset%20because%20all%20our%20effort%20was%20to%20help%20her%20attend%20school%20and%20she%20was%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20court%2C%20according%20to%20CBC.%20%26quot%3BI%20told%20her%20to%20cease%20the%20relationship%20with%20Danny%20Wong%20or%20wait%20until%20I'm%20dead.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPan%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fcanada%2Ftoronto%2Fjennifer-pan-sentenced-to-life-without-parole-for-25-years-1.2930113%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esentenced%20in%20January%202015%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20along%20with%20three%20of%20her%20co-accused%2C%20including%20Wong%20and%20Crawford.%20They%20were%20found%20guilty%20of%20fir