.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c673b743bb77284ba592f0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22609%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETesla%20announced%20layoffs%20on%20Sunday%20night.%3Cp%3EJustin%20Sullivan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOn%20Sunday%20night%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-ceo-elon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20sent%20a%20company-wide%20email%20to%20Tesla%20staff%20announcing%20a%20workforce%20reduction%20of%20more%20than%2010%25.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20laid-off%20Tesla%20worker%20said%20they%20moved%20about%206%20months%20ago%20for%20the%20job%20before%20being%20let%20go.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20moved%20cross-country%20after%20Tesla%20offered%20them%20a%20stipend%20to%20do%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20a%20former%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-history-founders%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETesla%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20employee%20who%20was%20laid%20off%20on%20Sunday%20night%20and%20requested%20anonymity%20to%20protect%20their%20privacy.%20Business%20Insider%20has%20verified%20their%20identity%20and%20employment.%20A%20spokesperson%20for%20Tesla%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20at%20Tesla%20as%20a%20commercial%20field%20services%20technician%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20I%20handled%20the%20troubleshooting%20and%20maintenance%20for%20Tesla's%20energy%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20out%20with%20the%20company%20in%20California%20and%20since%20have%20moved%20twice%20while%20working%20for%20Tesla.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20just%20moved%20across%20the%20country%20for%20the%20job%20six%20months%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20transferred%20me%20to%20one%20of%20its%20southern%20regions%20to%20service%20its%20energy%20department.%20The%20company%20needed%20someone%20in%20the%20region%20and%20hadn't%20had%20anybody%20on%20the%20ground%20there%20for%20over%20a%20year.%20People%20had%20to%20fly%20out%20to%20the%20area%20periodically%20to%20service%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20while%2C%20I%20was%20flying%20out.%20For%20like%20a%20period%20of%20three%20months%2C%20I%20was%20two%20weeks%20on%2C%20two%20weeks%20off%2C%20just%20picking%20up%20the%20slack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20Tesla%20asked%20me%20if%20I'd%20consider%20moving%20out%20there%20with%20my%20wife.%20I%20told%20them%20I'd%20only%20consider%20it%20if%20they%20paid%20for%20our%20move.%20They%20ended%20up%20helping%20with%20the%20relocation%20process%20and%20offered%20a%20stipend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20packed%20up%20and%20left%20in%20about%20a%20week.%20We%20sold%20most%20of%20our%20stuff%20and%20rented%20a%20big%20U-Haul%20to%20drive%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20was%20completely%20blindsided%20when%20I%20woke%20up%20on%20Monday%20morning%20to%20the%20layoff%20notice.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20woke%20up%20on%20Monday%20morning%2C%20trying%20to%20clock%20in%20to%20work.%20And%20my%20phone%20said%20something%20along%20the%20lines%20of%3A%20password%20error%2C%20contact%20IT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20went%20to%20my%20laptop%20to%20try%20to%20log%20in%20and%20I%20was%20locked%20out%20of%20my%20computer%20too%2C%20with%20the%20IT%20number%20right%20there%20on%20the%20screen.%20I%20called%20IT%20and%20they%20said%20I%20needed%20to%20contact%20HR.%20Then%20I%20went%20to%20my%20personal%20email%20account%20and%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-sent-tesla-employees-email-announcing-layoffs-read-memo-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaw%20an%20email%20from%20Tesla%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20was%20sent%20out%20overnight.%20It%20was%20that%20generic%20letter%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20other%20people%20have%20said%20they%20got.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20doing%20well%20and%20receiving%20positive%20feedback%20from%20my%20managers.%20In%20that%20layoff%20letter%20they%20said%20the%20cuts%20were%20due%20to%20redundancy%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20feel%20like%20my%20role%20was%20redundant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20like%20Tesla%20could%20have%20handled%20the%20layoffs%20better.%20It%20was%20impersonal%20and%20abrupt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20feel%20like%20we're%20kind%20of%20stuck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20in%20a%20town%20where%20I%20probably%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20find%20a%20lot%20of%20other%20opportunities%20without%20having%20to%20commute%20around%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half%20to%20work%20both%20ways%20because%20of%20the%20rural%20location.%20We're%20also%20far%20away%20from%20family%20and%20without%20a%20nearby%20support%20system%20to%20help%20us%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20lost%20some%20of%20our%20safety%20net%20when%20we%20moved.%20We%20rented%20a%20home%20that%20was%20well%20within%20our%20budget%20with%20my%20Tesla%20pay%2C%20but%20less%20so%20now%20that%20I've%20been%20laid%20off.%20Now%20we're%20stuck%20in%20the%20lease%20for%20six%20more%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20moved%20for%20Tesla%20we%20didn't%20take%20it%20lightly%2C%20but%20we%20didn't%20expect%20this.%20Leaving%20was%20tough%20because%20we'd%20been%20living%20near%20family.%20I%20have%20two%20children%2C%20a%2017-year-old%20and%20a%209-year-old%2C%20and%20we%20had%20to%20uproot%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20I%20feel%20like%20we%20rolled%20the%20dice%20and%20we've%20kind%20of%20shot%20ourselves%20in%20the%20foot%20as%20a%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20for%20Tesla%20or%20have%20a%20tip%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20the%20reporter%20via%20a%20non-work%20email%20and%20device%20at%20gkay%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%