5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhile%20cooking%20beef%2C%20the%20pan%20heated%20up%20evenly%20and%20gave%20it%20a%20nice%20crispy%20sear.%3Cp%3EConnie%20Chen%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20limited%20kitchen%20space%20but%20want%20to%20maximize%20your%20dinner%20possibilities%2C%20the%20Deep%20Cut%2C%20a%20hybrid%20of%20a%20saut%C3%A9%20pan%20and%20a%20skillet%2C%20is%20the%20pan%20you%20need%20to%20get.%20It's%20two%20inches%20deep%20to%20let%20you%20make%20saucy%20dishes%20without%20making%20a%20mess%2C%20but%20you%20can%20still%20do%20classic%20fries%20because%20of%20the%20sloped%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20handle%20design%20is%20beautiful%2C%20though%20it%20does%20sacrifice%20ergonomics%20for%20its%20unique%20outline%20look.%20If%20you%20have%20a%20strong%20wrist%20or%20don't%20mind%20a%20few%20minutes%20of%20discomfort%2C%20you'll%20be%20happy%20with%20the%20Deep%20Cut.%20Otherwise%2C%20I%20might%20suggest%20the%20less%20aesthetically%20pleasing%20but%20more%20functional%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-1303-20%26h%3Dbfd2597c0ac00d31b8f447848e747c83844d9fa8c76f781bfadc33a56e6e371e%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f42be7%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fgreat-jones-cookware-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fshareasale.com%252Fr.cfm%253Fb%253D999%2526u%253D1088116%2526m%253D88585%2526afftrack%253Dbiip_020520_great-jones-team-review%2526urllink%253Dsardelkitchen.com%25252Fcollections%25252Ffrontpage%25252Fproducts%25252Fsaute-pan%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESardel%20Saut%C3%A9%20Pan%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20first%20few%20times%20I've%20cooked%20with%20the%20Deep%20Cut%2C%20it%20feels%20sturdy%20and%20comfortable%20overall%2C%20and%20it%20seems%20like%20it'll%20face%20any%20everyday%20cooking%20task%20head-on.%20It%20also%20cleans%20easil