20is%20made%20from%C2%A0aluminized%20steel%2C%20which%20is%20more%20corrosion-resistant%20than%20steel%20and%20more%20heat-stable%20than%20aluminum%2C%20so%20it%20hasn't%20warped.%20There%20are%20also%20(presumably%20very%20thin)%20steel%20rods%20running%20through%20the%20pan%2C%20which%20help%20it%20keep%20its%20shape.%20When%20I%20broiled%20a%20whole%20fish%20in%20the%20pan%20and%20wanted%20to%20crisp%20up%20the%20dish%20before%20serving%20it%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20crank%20up%20the%20heat%20to%20well%20over%20500%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20without%20any%20warping.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20much%20as%20I%20like%20the%20performance%20of%20it%2C%20the%20Holy%20Sheet%20is%20just%20not%20an%20everyday%20sheet%20pan.%20I%20have%20used%20the%20Holy%20Sheet%20regularly%2C%20and%20it%20hasn't%20held%20up%20well.%20At%20this%20point%2C%20I%20need%20to%20do%20heavy%20scrubbing%20to%20thoroughly%20clean%20it%2C%20which%20damages%20the%20ceramic%20coating.%3Cem%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E%E2%80%94%20Owen%20Burke%2C%20Insider%20contributor%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fgreat-jones-cookware-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713299722000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661ecd9820b15f0ff428820f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fgreat-jones-cookware-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Great%20Jones%20makes%20colorful%20cookware%20that's%20beautiful%20and%20versatile.%20Here's%20what%20we%20think%20of%20the%20pots%20and%20pans%2C%20including%20the%20signature%20Dutchess%20oval%20oven.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22oburke%40businessinsider.com%20(Owen%20Burke)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fgreat-jones-cookware-review%22%2C%22cdn