%20Khan's%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20Deputy%20Inspector%20General%20of%20Police%2C%20Kutch%20West%2C%20Mahendra%20Bagadiya%2C%20said%20earlier%20in%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Mumbai%20Police%20official%20said%20the%20men%2C%20originally%20from%20Champaran%20in%20Bihar%2C%20travelled%20to%20Mumbai%20Central%20station%20on%20February%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20rented%20a%20house%20near%20Panvel%20city%20in%20Raigad%2C%20around%2013%20km%20away%20from%20Salman%20Khan's%20farmhouse%2C%20he%20said.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20not%20known%20whether%20they%20had%20conducted%20a%20recce%20of%20the%20farmhouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20they%20used%20their%20original%20Aadhaar%20cards%20for%20a%20rent%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20agreement%20was%20made%20with%20the%20house%20owner%20wherein%20the%20one-time%20deposit%20is%20fixed%20at%20Rs%2010%2C000%20and%20monthly%20rent%20at%20Rs%203%2C500%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20staying%20for%20a%20few%20days%20in%20Panvel%2C%20the%20duo%20travelled%20to%20Champaran%20on%20March%2018%20for%20Holi%20celebrations.%20They%20returned%20on%20April%201%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%202%2C%20Vicky%20Gupta%20purchased%20a%20second-hand%20motorcycle%20from%20a%20two-wheeler%20agent%20in%20Navi%20Mumbai%20for%20Rs%2024%2C000%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20days%2C%20a%20pistol%20to%20be%20used%20for%20firing%20was%20delivered%20to%20them%20in%20Mumbai%20by%20their%20operator%2C%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20had%20recovered%20a%20live%20round%20from%20the%20spot%20after%20the%20firing%20incident%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20April%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsidering%20the%20make%20of%20the%20round%2C%20police%20suspect%20a%20good%20quality%20weapon%20was%20used%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreliminary%20probe%20suggested%20that%20Pal%2C%20who%20was%20riding%20pillion%20on%20the%20motorcycle%2C%20opened%20fire%2C%20while%20Gupta%20remained%20in%20touch%20with%20gang%20members%20while%20riding%20the%20bike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20opening%20fire%2C%20they%20abandoned%20the%20bike%20near%20Mount%20Mary%20Church%20in%20Bandra%2C%20went%20to%20the%20local%20railway%20station%20and%20boarded%20a%20Borivali-bound%20local%20train%2C%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20alighted%20at%20Santacruz%20railway%20station%20and%20from%20Vakola%20area%2C%20they%20hired%20a%20car%20to%20go%20to%20Surat.%20From%20Surat%2C%20they%20travelled%20to%20Bhuj%20in%20a%20state%20transport%20bus%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20dumped%20the%20firearm%20used%20in%20the%20crime%20in%20a%20river%20while%20heading%20to%20Surat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPolice%20are%20trying%20to%20establish%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20person%20who%20provided%20the%20duo%20logistical%20support%20and%20money%20for%20their%20stay%20in%20Panvel%20and%20also%20for%20purchasing%20the%20bike%20and%20other%20expenses%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20how%20the%20breakthrough%20was%20achieved%2C%20Joint%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(crime)%20Lakhmi%20Gautam%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWith%20the%20help%20of%20human%20and%20technical%20intelligence%2C%20the%20crime%20branch%20team%20received%20information%20that%20the%20accused%20persons%20were%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20following%20which%20two%20teams%20were%20sent%20to%20nab%20them%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20there%20was%20a%20possibility%20that%20the%20accused%20persons%20were%20carrying%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20terrain%20of%20Bhuj%20was%20unknown%20to%20our%20officials%2C%20the%20Bhuj%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20was%20informed%20about%20the%20accused%20persons%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20team%20from%20the%20Bhuj%20crime%20branch%20joined%20Mumbai%20Police%20officials%20around%2060%20km%20away%20from%20Bhuj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20travelling%20around%2040%20kilometres%20farther%2C%20the%20two%20accused%20were%20nabbed%20by%20the%20team.%20They%20were%20brought%20to%20Mumbai%20this%20morning%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lakhmi%20Gautam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20official%20said%20the%20police%20first%20traced%20the%20original%20owner%20of%20the%20motorcycle%20to%20Kalamboli%20in%20Navi%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20said%20the%20owner%20directed%20them%20to%20the%20agent%2C%20who%20showed%20the%20documents%20submitted%20for%20the%20purchase%20of%20the%20bike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20these%20documents%2C%20which%20included%20a%20rent%20agreement%2C%20police%20contacted%20the%20house%20owner.%20The%20Aadhaar%20cards%20revealed%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20duo%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Lakhmi%20Gautam%20said%20there%20is%20good%20coordination%20among%20sister%20agencies%20as%20Mumbai%20Police%20and%20their%20Gujarat%20counterpart%20separately%20claimed%20credit%20for%20the%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713292440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F8q2vr518_salman-khan_120x90_16_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-cops-caught-men-who-opened-fire-outside-salman-khans-home-5457698%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20original%20Aadhaar%20cards%20submitted%20by%20two%20suspects%2C%20wanted%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20firing%20at%20actor%20Salman%20Khan's%20Bandra%20residence%2C%20for%20a%20rent%20agreement%20and%20bike%20purchase%20documents%20helped%20police%20to%20establish%20their%20identities%2C%20an%20official%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-n