e-political-posts-in-india-after-poll-bodys-takedown-order-5457253%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BVoters%20Intelligent%2C%20Look%20What%20Happened%20To%20Indira%20Gandhi%26quot%3B%3A%20Sam%20Pitroda%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20Overseas%20Congress%20Chairman%20of%C2%A0%20Sam%20Pitroda%20has%20expressed%20confidence%20that%20the%20Congress%20and%20INDIA%20bloc%20will%20do%20well%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20and%20said%20that%20Indian%20voters%20have%20a%20tendency%20to%20surprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet's%20wait%20for%20two%20months%20and%20we%20will%20know%20(results%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls).%20There%20is%20no%20need%20to%20predict%20right%20now%20what%20will%20happen.%20Indian%20voters%20have%20a%20tendency%20to%20surprise%20people.%20Look%20what%20happened%20to%20Mrs%20(Indira)%20Gandhi%20when%20she%20declared%20an%20Emergency.%20She%20was%20thrown%20out%20and%20then%20she%20was%20put%20back%20in.%20So%20don't%20underestimate%20the%20intelligence%20of%20Indian%20voters%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pitroda%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Indian%20voters%20feel%20they%20want%20to%20live%20in%20a%20democratic%20country%2C%20they%20want%20to%20live%20in%20a%20non-dictatorial%20environment%2C%20they%20want%20institutions%20to%20work%2C%20they%20want%20freedom%2C%20flexibility%2C%20they%20want%20to%20practice%20religion%20they%20like%2C%20they%20want%20to%20marry%20the%20one%20they%20want%20to%2C%20they%20want%20jobs%20to%20be%20created%2C%20they%20want%20inflation%20to%20be%20controlled%2C%20they%20will%20vote%20accordingly.%20So%20have%20some%20faith%20in%20Indian%20voters%20and%20not%20in%20pollsters%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20responding%20to%20a%20question%20about%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20Congress%2C%20especially%20in%20north%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pitroda%2C%20a%20former%20advisor%20to%20then%20Prime%20Minister%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20is%20considered%20close%20to%20the%20Nehru-Gandhi%20family%2C%20said%20Congress%20leaders%20are%20working%20hard%20to%20put%20up%20a%20good%20fight%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20say%20INDIA%20alliance%20is%20doing%20a%20reasonably%20good%20job.%20Mr%20Kharge%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20and%20many%20others%20in%20the%20Congress%20party%20are%20working%20hard%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pitroda%20said%20the%20Congress%20manifesto%20released%20earlier%20this%20month%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20perfect%20manifesto%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20people%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%20at%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20manifesto.%20Under%20the%20leadership%20of%20P%20Chidambaram%2C%20the%20manifesto%20was%20prepared.%20It%20is%20a%20good%20manifesto%20according%20to%20me%20but%20some%20people%20say%20it%20is%20not%20a%20good%20manifesto%2C%20it%20is%20a%20Communist%20manifesto.%20It%20depends%20on%20their%20perception.%20I%20don't%20think%20it%20is%20a%20Communist%20manifesto%2C%20it%20is%20humanistic.%20It%20is%20the%20right%20kind%20of%20values%20that%20Congress%20stands%20for.%20It%20is%20a%20perfect%20manifesto%20for%20the%20people%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pitroda%2C%20a%20technocrat%2C%20served%20as%20Chairman%20of%20Telecom%20Commission%20and%20headed%20India's%20National%20Knowledge%20Commission%20(2005-2009.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20will%20be%20held%20in%20seven%20phases%2C%20starting%20April%2019.%20The%20counting%20of%20votes%20is%20scheduled%20for%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713287580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-03%2Fk0pcivcg_sam-pitroda-pti-image-650_650x400_22_March_19.jpg%22%2C%22origi