-09%2F11%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1694420367-1733.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fpc-jeweller-gets-board-approval-to-raise-rs-2-000-cr-fund-via-rights-issue-124041601015_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22PC%20Jeweller%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20its%20board%20has%20approved%20a%20proposal%20to%20raise%20Rs%202%2C000%20crore%20through%20rights%20issues%20and%20preferential%20allotment%20of%20fully%20convertible%20warrants.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fpc-jeweller-gets-board-approval-to-raise-rs-2-000-cr-fund-via-rights-issue-124041601015_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fpc-jeweller-gets-board-approval-to-raise-rs-2-000-cr-fund-via-rights-issue-124041601015_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fpc-jeweller-gets-board-approval-to-raise-rs-2-000-cr-fund-via-rights-issue-124041601015_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bengaluru%20Woman%20Fined%20Rs%201.36%20Lakh%20For%20Violating%20Traffic%20Rules%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20in%20Bengaluru%20was%20fined%20Rs%201.36%20lakhs%20and%20her%20Honda%20Activa%20scooter%20was%20seized%20for%20breaking%20traffic%20laws%20regularly%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fauto%2Fbikes%2Fbengaluru-woman-rider-gets-rs-1-36-lakh-fine-honda-activa-scooter-seized%2Farticleshow%2F109315085.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20Of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Interestingly%2C%20the%20fine%20is%20much%20more%20than%20what%20her%20vehicle's%20cost.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20was%20seen%20tripling%20on%20a%20scooter%20without%20wearing%20a%20helmet%20in%20her%20latest%20violation.%20As%20per%20the%20outlet%2C%20she%20has%20violated%20the%20rules%20roughly%20270%20times.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20the%20violations%20included%20riding%20on%20the%20wrong%20side%20of%20the%20road%2C%20carrying%20a%20pillion%20ride%20without%20a%20helmet%2C%20riding%20without%20a%20helmet%2C%20using%20a%20phone%20while%20riding%2C%20and%20even%20jumping%20traffic%20signals.%20The%20CCTV%20cameras%20that%20were%20positioned%20across%20her%20regular%20path%20in%20Bengaluru%20recorded%20these%20offences.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20clear%20whether%20the%20woman%20has%20paid%20the%20fine%20and%20settled%20the%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20December%202023%2C%20a%20man%20in%20Bengaluru%20was%20served%20a%20notice%20by%20the%20traffic%20police%20to%20clear%20dues%20worth%20Rs%201.34%20lakh%20generated%20by%20his%20255%20traffic%20violations.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20in%20Deccan%20Herald%2C%20the%20man%20named%20Elumalai%20had%20accumulated%20the%20violations%20over%20a%20period%20of%20two%20years.%20His%20details%20came%20up%20when%20the%20Traffic%20management%20Centre%20(TMC)%20was%20looking%20for%20vehicles%20with%20a%20high%20number%20of%20traffic%20violations.%20The%20information%20was%20sent%20to%20police%20stations%20across%20the%20city.%20The%20traffic%20police%20personnel%20were%20asked%20to%20track%20down%20such%20vehicles%20and%20recover%20fines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20then%20started%20their%20investigation%20and%20found%20that%20a%20scooter%20registered%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Elumalai%2C%20a%20daily%20wager%2C%20had%20255%20traffic%20violations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20called%20to%20the%20police%20station%20and%20told%20about%20it.%20Elumalai%20told%20the%20police%20personnel%20that%20he%20was%20unaware%20of%20the%20intelligent%20traffic%20management%20system%20(ITMS)%20cameras%20installed%20across%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Deccan%20Herald%20report%20said%20that%20Elumalai%20