ion%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20excitement%20mirrors%20his%20when%20he%20first%20learnt%20about%20these%20iconic%20spots.%20Praise%20him%20for%20the%20extensive%20knowledge%20base%20he%20has%20put%20together%20and%20Johann%20is%20adamant%20that%20there%20is%20still%20a%20great%20deal%20he%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20yet%20explored.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20a%20sales%20manager%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20one%20might%20ask%20what%20geared%20him%20towards%20heritage%20storytelling.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20travel%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20answers.%C2%A0%20And%20so%2C%20storytelling%20was%20born%20out%20of%20serendipity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20trip%20is%20the%20best%20part%20for%20many%2C%20for%20Johann%20it%20was%20to%20return%20home%20to%20write%20about%20it.%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F328967%2Fheritage-walks-in-india-shillong-mumbai-bengaluru-hyderabad-delhi-travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheritage%20walks%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20what%20fascinated%20him%20the%20most.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20don%E2%80%99t%20we%20have%20something%20like%20this%20in%20Kochi%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20wondered.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20set%20the%20stage%20in%20Johann%E2%80%99s%20mind%20for%20the%20idea%20of%20heritage%20storytelling%2C%20the%20Kochi%20Heritage%20Project%20would%20take%20a%20few%20years%20to%20come%20into%20the%20picture.%20The%20gap%20was%20spent%20applying%20to%20storytelling%20positions%2C%20doing%20freelance%20travel%20projects%2C%20and%20conducting%20a%20few%20heritage%20walks%20around%20South%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20was%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20hours%20spent%20reading%20the%20books%20he%20had%20been%20stacking%20in%20his%20home%20library%20%E2%80%94%20that%20Johann%20decided%20this%20was%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20past%20needed%20a%20futu