20spending%20the%20past%20three%20decades%20of%20his%20life%20in%20the%20horticulture%20industry%2C%20Bhausaheb%20was%20itching%20to%20start%20his%20own%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20three%20children%20in%20school%2C%20Bhausaheb%E2%80%99s%20family%20was%20initially%20surprised%20by%20his%20decision.%20However%2C%20they%20were%20confident%20in%20his%20experience%2C%20knowledge%2C%20and%20strong%20determination%20to%20make%20the%20venture%20successful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20on%201%20March%2C%202020%2C%20he%20started%20a%20nursery%20business%20in%20Pune%20called%20%E2%80%98Greens%20and%20Blooms%E2%80%99%20with%20his%20friend%20Sharad%20Patil.%20The%20duo%20invested%20almost%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20of%20their%20own%20capital%20to%20start%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20luck%20would%20have%20it%2C%2023%20days%20later%2C%20the%20Government%20called%20for%20a%20nationwide%20lockdown%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F297444%2Fgupshup-ai-whatsapp-solution-helps-feed-millions-ngos-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecombat%20COVID-19%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Bhausaheb%E2%80%99s%20business%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296147%2Fhow-to-grow-orchids-at-home-delhi-gardener-shares-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrowing%20exotic%20flowers%2C%20such%20as%20orchids%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20anthuriums%2C%20involved%20a%20lot%20of%20imports.%20So%20with%20the%20lockdown%20imposed%2C%20his%20business%20was%20off%20to%20a%20rocky%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20lose%20hope.%20His%20tenacity%20and%20passion%20for%20floriculture%20inspired%20him%20to%20beat%20all%20odds%20and%20take%20his%20business%20to%20heights.%20This%20year%2C%20he%20earned%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs%202%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98It%E2%80%99s%20all%20in%20or%20noth