ese%20funds%20are%20created%20in%20a%20unique%20way%3A%2010%20percent%20of%20all%20homestays%E2%80%99%20income%20goes%20into%20a%20%E2%80%98village%20conservation%20fund%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20used%20by%20villagers%20for%20tree%20planting%2C%20garbage%20cleaning%2C%20and%20maintenance%20of%20their%20cultural%20heritage%2C%20such%20as%20mani%20walls%2C%20%3Cem%3Echortens%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20sacred%20juniper%20stands.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344962%2Fhow-to-start-a-homestay-in-india-rules-tips-from-owners-travel-business%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evillagers%20are%20encouraged%20to%20host%20guests%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20a%20rotational%20basis.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20done%20so%20that%20no%20single%20family%20can%20monopolise%20the%20tourists.%20Because%20if%20that%20were%20to%20happen%2C%20it%20would%20create%20a%20disharmony%20in%20the%20village.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Namgail%20shares%2C%20the%20tourism%20model%20has%20been%20so%20successful%20that%20people%20across%20the%20Himalayas%20have%20taken%20inspiration%20from%20it%20and%20are%20replicating%20it.%20But%20regulation%20is%20important%2C%20he%20emphasises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20evening%20settles%20over%20Ladakh%2C%20the%20snow%20is%20tinged%20with%20a%20mix%20of%20blue%20and%20orange%2C%20a%20blend%20of%20the%20hues%20of%20the%20setting%20sun%20and%20dusk.%20As%20the%20locals%20go%20into%20their%20homes%2C%20bolt%20their%20doors%2C%20and%20warn%20the%20children%20to%20stay%20inside%2C%20the%20silent%20rustle%20of%20leaves%20goes%20unheard.%20So%20does%20the%20slither%20in%20the%20bushes%20and%20the%20shadow%20of%20a%20feline%20beginning%20its%20prowl.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712827631000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsnow-leopard-conservancy--